{"tid":1809430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"811維園第一次黑警喬裝拉到既手足獲撒銷擔保無條件釋放！","createTime":"2020-01-03T05:53:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T17:28:12.000Z","uid":22556,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"e03ce5eff3dd849b481667cc996aa9e246a06568","tid":1809430,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T05:53:57.000Z","msg":"【#被捕支援】<br />\n<br />\n2019年8月11日晚上10時許，銅鑼灣有身穿黑衣、帶上口罩、喬裝成示威者的不知明人士，連同速龍小隊在軒尼詩道衝前毆打襲擊多人，繼而作出非法拘捕。傷者輕則頭破血流，重則骨折斷手，及後更被警方拖延送院，阻礙救援。<br />\n<br />\n早前已有同案成功踢保，今日警方主動提出撤銷擔保，餘下被捕人士無須再到警署報到，獲無條件釋放。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">註：此案與暴動罪相關個案的案情及性質並不類同，不能比較及參考。踢保失敗或會換來更嚴厲的法庭保釋條件，請因應個人情況及查詢專業的法律意見才決定行動。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n國民支援<br />\n2020年1月3日<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n「#國民支援」目的是建立一個人道支援網絡，包括：<br />\n一、尋求支援（法律、生活、醫療等）：9030-2853（鄭錦滿）；<br />\n二、提供支援（工作、實習、捐款等）：5596-8181（Kina）。<br />\n<br />\n#Telegram：@blesshongkongmatchingscheme<br />\n#國泰民安人道支援 Telegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/blesshkmatchingscheme\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fblesshkmatchingscheme&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7HXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=79dccb47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/blesshkmatchingscheme</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/111284017035418/posts/120589059438247/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F111284017035418%2Fposts%2F120589059438247%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7HXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=58ac9f1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/111284017035418/posts/120589059438247/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"1ac5c8bdaf765be1138591f03309974ea775ca98","tid":1809430,"uid":116054,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T05:55:32.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，咁即係無故傷人啦警曱<br />\n<br />\n眾籌追究佢老母臭閪"},{"pid":"96ee388cff3024d141cea6f40af605a4fee8201a","tid":1809430,"uid":155224,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"ci